name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 65: East Coast Socks

content.html:
Dear Internet, On this weeks show, well, I wasn’t on it. So I’m not exactly sure what it is discussed. I have my shots and was away with my family. I do they talk about a hulk, buying close, and crushin on boys. Stay gold, XOXO We are a new show, and would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick Bristow, Jennifer Cheek, Michael DiMauro, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
